graph TB
    subgraph Operator["OGX K8s Operator"]
        direction TB
        Controller["OGXServer Reconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Webhook["Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS"]
        KustomizeEngine["Embedded Kustomize Engine<br/>Manifest Rendering"]
        LegacyAdoption["Legacy Adoption System<br/>v1alpha1 → v1beta1 Migration"]

        Controller -->|renders manifests via| KustomizeEngine
        Controller -->|migrates resources via| LegacyAdoption
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    %% CRDs
    User[Data Scientist / Admin] -->|creates| OGXServerCR["OGXServer CR<br/>(ogx.io/v1beta1)"]
    LegacyUser[Legacy User] -->|creates| LlamaStackCR["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)"]
    OGXServerCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LlamaStackCR -->|adopted by| LegacyAdoption

    %% Managed Resources
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment["Deployment<br/>OGX Server Pod"]
    Controller -->|creates| Service["Service<br/>ClusterIP {port}/TCP"]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy["NetworkPolicy"]
    Controller -->|creates| PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim"]
    Controller -->|creates| HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
    Controller -->|creates| PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
    Controller -->|creates| IngressRes["Ingress<br/>(when externalAccess enabled)"]
    Controller -->|creates| ConfigMap["ConfigMap<br/>config.yaml"]

    %% Managed OGX Server
    Deployment -->|runs| OGXServer["OGX Server Container<br/>Distribution Image"]

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|TLS certs from| CertProvider["cert-manager /<br/>OpenShift service-ca"]
    Controller -->|metrics via| KubeRBACProxy["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP"]
    KubeRBACProxy -->|scraped by| Prometheus["Prometheus"]
    Controller -->|reads| CABundle["odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap"]

    %% OGX Server Connections
    OGXServer -->|inference| RemoteProviders["Remote Providers<br/>(vLLM, OpenAI, Azure,<br/>Bedrock, VertexAI, Watsonx)"]
    OGXServer -->|vector I/O| VectorDBs["Vector DBs<br/>(PGVector, Milvus, Qdrant)"]
    OGXServer -->|file storage| S3["S3-compatible Storage"]

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style KustomizeEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LegacyAdoption fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OGXServerCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style LlamaStackCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Service fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style NetworkPolicy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style PVC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style HPA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style PDB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style IngressRes fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ConfigMap fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OGXServer fill:#50c878,stroke:#333
    style RemoteProviders fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style VectorDBs fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style CertProvider fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
